<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sake-n">sake <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /seɪk/    美 /seɪk/  </p>
<p>[常用于以下惯用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="for-the-sake-of-sb-sth">for the sake of sb / sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为了某人 / 某事物的缘故 (for sb’s / sth’s sake):</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He moved to the seaside for the sake of his health. 
他为了健康而搬去海边。</p></div></div>